1. Kupio sam *1 kg* brašna u prodavnici. (I bought *1 kg* of flour at the store.)
2. Hleb košta *150 din/kg*. (Bread costs *150 din/kg*.)
3. Pokupio sam *10 kg* jabuka u voćnjaku. (I picked up *10 kg* of apples in the orchard.)
4. Treba mi *1/2 kg* šećera za kolače. (I need *1/2 kg* of sugar for the cakes.)
5. Prevozio sam teret od *500 kg* kamionom. (I transported a load of *500 kg* with a truck.)
6. Ova vagarska jedinica se koristi za merenje mase i zove se *kilogram (kg)*. (This weighing unit is used for measuring mass and it's called *kilogram (kg)*.)
7. Na njihovom jelovniku napisano je da je pileći file *200g* (a naš *1/5 kg*). (On their menu, it's written that the chicken fillet is *200g* (which is *1/5 kg* of ours).)
8. Sportisti često treniraju sa tegovima teškim *10 kg* ili više. (Athletes often train with weights of *10 kg* or more.)